1 Dependancies

libssl (0.9.7)

1.1 For developpement version:

libcunit1-dev
doxygen (for code documentation)

2 Compilation

The following steps will install agrego-local and agrego-distant. Today there is no way
to install only one using 'make install'.

./bootstrap
./configure
make
make install


For debian like systems this package are required:
 * libssl-dev
 * for unit test libcunit1-dev

